translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 他の項目に隠れてるけど、この数字にはならない
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: It's hidden under other items, but it doesn't come to this number.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「まあ！　カチューシャさん。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "My! Katiusha-san.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 私だって業者さんに何度も聞き返したのよ？
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I also asked the vendor many times, you know?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: そしたら相手も無理ですって泣き出しちゃって
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Then they said it was impossible and even started crying.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ここの所、闇ルートで竜角惨が定期的に流れてる。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Lately, the Dragon Horns have been flowing regularly through black market routes.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 聞いたのが業者なら、たぶん工場元か、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: If the ones I heard it from are vendors, it's probably from the factory or,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: それと組んで横流ししてる奴がいる
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: someone partnering with them to illegally resell.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「あらやだ、そうなの？　良くないわねぇ……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Oh my, is that so? That's not good at all...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ハピネスさんならご存じかしら……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I wonder if Happiness-san knows about this...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「次は？」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Next?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「えーっと……今日、他にあったかな……」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Umm... Was there anything else today...?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「こちらで事前に伺った分ですと、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: According to what we heard beforehand,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 今ので最後かと……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: that should be the last...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「ずいぶん、はよ終わったなぁ……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: That ended pretty quickly...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「……終わりね？　じゃあ」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: ...That's all? Then,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「あらまあ。お茶しようと思ったのに、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Oh my. I was thinking of having tea,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 忙しないのねぇ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: but you're so busy.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「……もしかして、カチューシャさんって
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: ...Could it be that Katiusha-san is

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 物凄く優秀……？」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: incredibly talented...?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「人類社会の裏側のボスみたいな
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Like a boss behind human society,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 女性ですしなぁ……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: and she's a woman, after all...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「……あんま、気ぃ許したないんやけど……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: ...I don't really want to let my guard down though...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「ま、ラクなら俺ぁそれで構わないがねぇ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Well, if it's easier, I don't mind that.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「でも、早く終わらせて……どうするんでしょう？
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: But finishing quickly... what are you going to do then?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ランスさんの所に戻るんですよね……？
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: You're going back to Rance-san's place, right...?
...Hmmmm...?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「あ！　カチューシャだ！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Ah! It's Katiusha!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「あ、な、何よ……偶然ね」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Uh, wh-what is it... It's just a coincidence."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「ここで会ったが百年目！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Meeting here marks our hundredth time!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 遊ぶぜーーーー！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Let's playyyyy!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「っ……そ、それならもう少し女の子らしく……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "T-then, maybe act a little more like a girl...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: あ、こら、手ぇ引っ張るなっ……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Ah, hey, don't pull my hand like that..."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ランスに命じられた帰還までの間、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: During the time until returning as ordered by Rance,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: カチューシャは、ナギに振り回された。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Katiusha was swept around by Nagi.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「お嬢様……僕と……僕と一緒に、逃げましょう！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "My lady... with me... let's run away together!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 旦那様方には内緒で……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Without telling the masters...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「まあ……！　でも、その、大丈夫、かしらぁ……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Oh my... but, um, will that be okay...?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: パパたち、きっと心配するわぁ……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Papa and the others will surely worry...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「二人のためです！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: It's for the two of us!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 旦那様方には、後で説明すれば……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: We'll explain to the masters later...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ん、んん〜……そう、ねぇ……そう、かしら……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Hmm, mmm... is that so... I wonder...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「お願いします、お嬢様……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Please, my lady...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 家を離れるのは……やっぱり、少し考えさせて。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Leaving home... please let me think about it a little longer.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 私……外のことは何も分からない、小娘だもの
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I'm just a young girl who knows nothing about the outside world.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「お嬢様……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "My lady...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: パパやママにも、しっかり話して分かって貰うわ。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I'll talk properly with Papa and Mama and make them understand.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 大丈夫よ。説得してみせるわ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: It's okay. I'll try to convince them.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: …………分かりました。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: ...I understand.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: しかし、私はもう、お屋敷では会えない……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: However, I won't be able to see you at the mansion anymore...

translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Oh my... but, um, will that be okay...?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: パパたち、きっと心配するわぁ……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Papa and the others will surely worry...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「二人のためです！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: It's for the two of us!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 旦那様方には、後で説明すれば……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: We'll explain to the masters later...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ん、んん〜……そう、ねぇ……そう、かしら……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Hmm, mmm... is that so... I wonder...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「お願いします、お嬢様……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Please, my lady...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 家を離れるのは……やっぱり、少し考えさせて。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Leaving home... please let me think about it a little longer.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 私……外のことは何も分からない、小娘だもの
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I'm just a young girl who knows nothing about the outside world.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「お嬢様……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "My lady...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: パパやママにも、しっかり話して分かって貰うわ。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I'll talk properly with Papa and Mama and make them understand.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 大丈夫よ。説得してみせるわ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: It's okay. I'll try to convince them.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: …………分かりました。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: ...I understand.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: しかし、私はもう、お屋敷では会えない……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: However, I won't be able to see you at the mansion anymore...
